{"tid":114452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當年嘅lesser evil: 民主回歸","createTime":"2017-02-09T18:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T05:12:51.000Z","uid":37300,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21d09ce0145166003e6659332fb302f9b205b695","tid":114452,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】民主黨創黨主席李柱銘昨出席香港基督徒學會講座，談及年輕人對泛民主派的批評。李透露曾有年輕人問他為何不爭取港獨，<span style=\"color: red;\">他坦言當年民主回歸是沒有選擇中的選擇，冀大眾別太輕易把責任歸咎上一代</span>；至於2047年本港可否獨立，他認為可以討論，但籲市民思考在一國一制和獨立之間，會否有其他選擇。<br />\n<br />\n「子彈一嚟會點呢？」<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘昨於講座中憶述雨傘運動時，有19歲年輕人問他為何不於中英談判時期爭取港獨，李坦言1980年代，加拿大、澳洲、歐洲多國普遍為自身利益，支持本港民主回歸，<span style=\"color: red;\">縱使他當時明白獨立對本港最好，但終因為現實選擇回歸路，並要求中共嚴格執行一國兩制，「搞革命，子彈一嚟，會點呢？」</span><br />\n<br />\n李無奈指，本港回歸後一直在鳥籠內走民主路，中共至今更違背在港實踐普選的承諾，「呢件事佢（中共）一定要做，<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋會不斷指摘佢</span>」。坊間有輿論欲爭取2047年實行港獨，李柱銘認為可討論，但必須思考港獨後如何處理食水、食物問題，又反問：「喺一國一制同獨立中間，有冇其他選擇呢？」<br />\n<br />\n近年某些激進派的行動一次比一次激烈，李柱銘認為他們是為了爭取選票，又引孫中山推翻滿清為例，指若真正發動革命，會將事情保密。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160523/19623673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160523%2F19623673&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FcjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4c18fb3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160523%2F19623673&h=046d58e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160523/19623673</a>"},{"pid":"da755285a63962b6481310c754a167c3dc144f06","tid":114452,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:40:11.000Z","msg":"英國佬顧住自己利益啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4981c98f5999068f8303885c275ea126793a8862","tid":114452,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國佬顧住自己利益啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年Lesser evil嘅結果就係今日咁"},{"pid":"7c7d159a95f17aa3c36365678c0e431349d4fb3f","tid":114452,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:54:30.000Z","msg":"根本呢班人係真心想香港被中國管治<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1246b34998a3a120c7978047e9649863e936dc6f","tid":114452,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T21:50:37.000Z","msg":"點樣唔好將責任輕易推畀上一代呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港新一代想亡羊補牢你地又出黎阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ad208c2a924f821e12415bc9ea0760d78957fb","tid":114452,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T21:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣唔好將責任輕易推畀上一代呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港新一代想亡羊補牢你地又出黎阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢篇舊文旨在話俾大家知富有中國特色的lesser evil會出咩結果"},{"pid":"18d8196e75e0428f4ee05fe9bdea640a9f4302ab","tid":114452,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:49:55.000Z","msg":"經歷咁多野香港人都無乜點進步過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cce9cdbf6902bd81928f920ef231e507b43da1","tid":114452,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經歷咁多野香港人都無乜點進步過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做人唔可以太好記性"},{"pid":"9cd8613226f501c699f00cdbe65880d7529c538c","tid":114452,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本呢班人係真心想香港被中國管治<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最終目標係建設民主中國"},{"pid":"31a9d5096b644d307072d27143dc8f8b34c0a865","tid":114452,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img